{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"92b03bef82","title":"周恩来接见卫生部领导同志的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fbf7ab58a8","index":0,"year":1970,"month":12,"day":28,"articleId":"92b03bef82","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"李震","id":"155c01ead4","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"清查五·一六","id":"a0d5508956","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d9e2b8864b","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见卫生部领导同志的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f505574cd","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：1970年12月28日凌晨1-4时〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8cfeec753","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：孙正专案组的报告，要罪状定实，不定实就不行，不落实就不行。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8926ab1412","type":"paragraph","text":"（汇报：杜南交代孙正组织“五·一六”是1967年7月23日晚上八点左右……。陆纯祥等三人交代是五月，但情节一样。）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5eb65b24be","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：时间不是主要的，主要看情节。“五·一六”主要是性质，反革命性质。“五·一六”、“六·一六”时间是次要的，不然永远跟着孙正、杜南牵着鼻子走。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d72fbbd59","type":"paragraph","text":"先念：谈到杜南搞档案资料，收集中央材料……。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3886b739ea","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这一段要批，到7.23才反无产阶级司令部？实际还早，1966年8月就开始了。许多事，历史要联系起来看。传单看过没有？孙正批了报销，矛头指向无产阶级司令部，表面上对钱信忠，我们警惕了这件事。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b3b73ff603","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：交事实不要打叉叉，不要注解。打叉叉有一个不打，就含糊其意，增加自己捆起手脚来，谈他的原话。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b90fbc1523","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：任鸿来何时死的？去年10月来，今年二月自杀，搞专案的问题，总是一种麻痹，一种搞神秘化。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33cd8d5fe1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：……叫嚷“无产阶级司令部也可以炮打”，抓住这句话就可以斗他。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fcaee22c2d","type":"paragraph","text":"李震：不在全部，不在多，在于精，不在广而在于准。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bcdc0d8780","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：定案，要说得准，很清楚。（举了骆宾王斗武则天，话并不多）只要两件清，八件清不要，要稳准狠。刘少奇不过只抓了他三件大事。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dec007619c","type":"paragraph","text":"第一步突出“五·一六”，杜南说他是顾问，他不需要参加，反革命阴谋集团操纵者可以说，也可以说是幕后的。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c8b7412c85","type":"paragraph","text":"说明：这是追记材料，很不完整。我们去卫生部军管会学习清查“五·一六”经验得到大力支持，给我们看了中央首长讲话的精神，但再三叮嘱是记录稿不要抄，因此只是凭看了以后记得的精神追记一些。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92b03bef82","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}